											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Suddenly the general takes a thrown spear through the abdomen. She collapses, struggling to get back up. Her remaining troops raise weapons -&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- a mass of enthralled Baldurians surround them from several directions. The gith are hopelessly outnumbered. The gith general, hunched over and mortally wounded, raises her scimitar and snarls defiantly.&#xD;&#xA;" />
